<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a2930; line-height: 1.6"
  >
    <p>Dear <%= customerName %>,</p>

    <p>
      This is a gentle reminder that your Ellcworth shipping quote is ready and
      awaiting your response.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Reference:</strong> <%= referenceNo %><br />
      <strong>Route:</strong> <%= originPort %> to <%= destinationPort %><br />
      <strong>Total:</strong> <%= currency %> <%= total %><br />
      <strong>Valid until:</strong> <%= validUntil %>
    </p>

    <p>
      If you would like to proceed, or if you would like us to make any
      adjustments, please reply to this email and our team will assist promptly.
    </p>

    <p>
      Kind regards,<br />
      Ellcworth Express
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
